Cell["\<\
xAct is no longer needed for background calculations, replace coordinate \
functions of the form \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote] r[ ] \[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] \
with regular symbols \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote] r \[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]. This \
will prevent conflicts with standard Mathematica operations. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.955587603472006*^9, 3.9555877096466303`*^9}, 
   3.955588080049529*^9, {3.964335379027255*^9, 
